{"tid":615842,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"睇挑戰者一號前面對情侶嘈住哂","createTime":"2018-04-03T17:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T15:07:34.000Z","uid":18521,"like":41,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"52dbc92ee62cf03b502f040be1f01a05d8f88eff","tid":615842,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T17:05:48.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇睇下挑戰者一號<br />\n去到尾段 男女主角𡃶𡃶<br />\n前面對情侶無啦啦又係到𡃶<br />\n我真係心諗<br />\n𡃶乜撚野<br />\n仲要𡃶出聲 D唔知乜撚吸吮聲<br />\n嘈撚住哂<br />\n睇戲就咪撚嘈住人啦<br />\n我屌佢老母呀？<br />\n好啦 散場<br />\n我見到前面係個南亞仔<br />\n加個鬼妹呀！！！！！！！<br />\n係白滑鬼妹<br />\n係高級高質白種人<br />\n鬼妹仔<br />\n點解<br />\n點解個南亞仔有得晚晚享受佢白滑嫩汁鮑<br />\n點解個黑過墨汁嘅南亞仔<br />\n有得狠狠地品嚐到個鬼妹嘅一線粉紅鮑魚<br />\n點解佢有得屌！！！！！<br />\n點解呀！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/010453_b30a8d07316ce7e14bdcce976a71c8f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F010453_b30a8d07316ce7e14bdcce976a71c8f4.jpg&h=5e014469&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be02a9b50838944c6cb88459b06a5eec6933311c","tid":615842,"uid":115655,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"崇洋港男好撚低賤"},{"pid":"9fc784aee3862f0712e8ab043b09b67d18c1400b","tid":615842,"uid":64469,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T18:19:39.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係好可怕"},{"pid":"1876658e43995fc86a19086a524352112431c5ba","tid":615842,"uid":18241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"be02a9b50838944c6cb88459b06a5eec6933311c","tid":615842,"uid":115655,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"崇洋港男好撚低賤"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:22:37.000Z","msg":"崇中直頭低賤中既xo"},{"pid":"91020ef1e3c6b74485a16cff7384d73904decbe2","tid":615842,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be02a9b50838944c6cb88459b06a5eec6933311c","tid":615842,"uid":115655,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTi